title: Raw for Dessert: Easy Delights for Everyone - Jennifer Cornbleet
description:
Now you can have your cake and eat it too! You can stay vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, or just plain health-conscious and still eat delicious cakes, pies, compotes, crumbles, custards, sorbets, ice creams, cookies, and candies!

Jennifer Cornbleet, author of the best selling Raw Food Made Easy for 1 or 2 People, shares her favorite easy no-bake treats. Learn how to:

Avoid white sugar, white flour, dairy products, trans-fats, saturated fats, and processed foods
Make easy-to-follow recipes quickly and affordably
Enjoy desserts for every occasion: Summer Berry Compote, Caramel Apple Stacks, Creme Brulee, Pineapple Upside Down Cake, Chocolate Cupcakes, Coconut Cream Pie, Tropical Ambrosia Tart, Pine Nut Caramels, Concord Grape Sorbet, Cookies n Cream Ice Cream, Knockout Brownie Sundae
